{"tid":1019022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[頭先我勁暈]#林明禎 IU 宮脇咲良 紅女巫 2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強首回合投選專區","createTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:05:30.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb771fa828efd26beb3e2995c4802a4a6c2f3436","tid":1019022,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n林明禎 v IU<br />\n宮脇咲良@HKT48 v Elizabeth Olsen<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86722cf34b709d926d4ccada5a0b4d5fe2cb6f0c","tid":1019022,"uid":92376,"like":66,"dislike":168,"score":-102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-2-13 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bNNoBqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbNNoBqP.png&h=f6ae6b76&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ASvY9Te.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FASvY9Te.png&h=6d98d5ee&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mS94Fjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmS94Fjr.png&h=c47132c2&s={SIZE}\" />林明禎 v 